<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dynamic Landing Page</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/index.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@10"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>

    <!-- Include Toastr CSS and JavaScript -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/latest/toastr.min.css" />
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/toastr.js/latest/toastr.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Cab Booking</h1>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">Welcome to Our World</h2>
            <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">Experience the future of web design with us.</p>
            @* <a href="#services" class="btn-primary"></a> *@
            <a  asp-area="" asp-controller="User" asp-action="LoginandSignup"><button type="button" class="btn-primary">Explore Our Services</button></a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Key Features</h2>
            <div class="feature">
                <i class="fas fa-car animate__animated animate__pulse"></i>
                <h3>Large Fleet of Vehicles</h3>
                <p>We offer a wide selection of vehicles to meet your needs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <i class="fas fa-clock animate__animated animate__pulse"></i>
                <h3>24/7 Availability</h3>
                <p>Our services are available round the clock for your convenience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <i class="fas fa-map-marker animate__animated animate__pulse"></i>
                <h3>Real-time GPS Tracking</h3>
                <p>Track your cab in real-time using our GPS technology.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <div class="service">
                <i class="fas fa-taxi animate__animated animate__zoomIn"></i>
                <h3>Local Rides</h3>
                <p>Quick and affordable transportation within the city.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <i class="fas fa-plane animate__animated animate__zoomIn"></i>
                <h3>Airport Transfers</h3>
                <p>Efficient rides to and from the airport.</p>
            </div>            <div class="service">
                <i class="fas fa-users animate__animated animate__zoomIn"></i>
                <h3>Group Travel</h3>
                <p>Transportation solutions for groups and events.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">

        <div class="container1">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="left-side">
                    <div class="address details">
                        <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                        <div class="text-one">Contact</div>
                        <div class="text-one">Us</div>
                        <div class="text-two">Form</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="phone details">
                        <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i>
                        <div class="topic">Phone</div>
                        <div class="text-one">+0098 9893 5647</div>
                        <div class="text-two">+0096 3434 5678</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="email details">
                        <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        <div class="topic">Email</div>
                        <div class="text-one">vivekkumarava1@gmail.com</div>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="right-side">
                    <div class="topic-text">Contact US</div>
                    <p>If you have any work from me or any types of quries related to my tutorial, you can send me message from here. It's my pleasure to help you.</p>
                    <form asp-action="Index" asp-controller="User" method="post">
                        <div class="input-box">
                            <input asp-for="Name" type="text" id="Name" placeholder="Enter your name">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-box">
                            <input  asp-for="Email" type="text" id="Email" placeholder="Enter your email">
                        </div>

                        <div class="input-box message-box">
                            <input asp-for="Message" type="text" id="Message" placeholder="Enter your Message">
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn btn-dark">
                            <input type="submit" value="Send Now">
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
